{"tid":107683,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測) 太空潛航者 撕裂地平線 鐵血戰士S","createTime":"2017-02-04T15:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T19:52:59.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"899ed622f0dc1ac79438c8ef7de478a9c3014715","tid":107683,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:31:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=27911789\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b1ae5a10\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a8/Passengers_2016_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa8%2FPassengers_2016_Poster.jpg&h=79c0662d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/8c/Event_horizon_ver1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F8c%2FEvent_horizon_ver1.jpg&h=368d580f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.星艦「阿瓦隆號」（Avalon）搭載5000多名殖民者前往行星「家園II號」（Homestead II），這趟旅程需花費120年時間。殖民者和乘務組都睡在小艙內休眠，但飛船途經一個大型小行星帶時，護盾嚴重受損，引發故障，提前90年喚醒機械工程師吉姆&middot;普雷斯頓（克里斯&middot;普瑞特 飾）。<br />\n<br />\n過了一年的孤獨生活，只有仿真機器人調酒師亞瑟（麥可&middot;辛 飾）的陪伴，沮喪的吉姆曾想過自殺。某日，他在休眠艙中找到年輕貌美的奧蘿拉&middot;朗恩（珍妮佛&middot;勞倫斯 飾），視頻資料顯示她是一位幽默的作家。歷經手動喚醒奧羅拉的道德思想鬥爭，吉姆最終喚醒了她，聲稱是休眠艙出故障導致的。奧蘿拉害怕自己星艦還沒有抵達「家園II號」便逐漸衰老死去，跟吉姆一樣竭力嘗試重新休眠未果。最終，她接受了事實，開始撰寫一本關於個人經歷的書。吉姆和奧蘿拉越走越近，成為戀人<br />\n<br />\n2.西元2040年，政府秘密製造的「Event Horizon號」太空船，要以新研發的重力驅動系統，製造出人造黑洞以進行時空重疊，可瞬間跳躍至數光年甚至數千光年以外之地，用來縮短太空探索時間的新科技。但該船在啟動首次的重力跳躍後，便一去不回，直到2047年才重新現身於海王星附近..<br />\n<br />\n11 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3317b0c7751e8c47ada9544811cc2a5f1c5c0c5f","tid":107683,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/kason2047/1430275149-261290301_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fkason2047%2F1430275149-261290301_l.jpg&h=824f4309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一道極強的亮光，將分處五大洲的8個人帶到了一片未知所在。他們身背降落傘從高空墜落，繼而落入一望無邊的雨林。這群人中有車臣部隊戰士，以色列國防軍，墨西哥特種 部隊成員，FBI通緝的要犯，日本黑幫稻川會頭目以及一名與其他人格格不入的醫生。他們彼此互不相識，也不知道為何被帶到了這片陌生叢林。在羅伊斯 &middot;布隆迪Adrien Brody飾）的帶領下，眾人開始朝制高點進發，最終發現他們竟然置於在一顆外星球中。與此同時，兇猛邪惡的猛獸接連向他們襲來，羅伊斯意識到，他們不過 是一群外星生物選出的獵物，而這片雨林正是外星人的狩獵場"},{"pid":"2e41327c41d42b04ac4f789e2a921ce3eaabc377","tid":107683,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd18dd771d5aeec5bdc87decfe846f48c80a156","tid":107683,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b07d039678678ad99da8786e1040fdca44a60a","tid":107683,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308eb34bc07f160d07c40166b6e062aff91d2c95","tid":107683,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T18:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfbc0c72da379c08413bff2bc1c4e6aa3cf644e","tid":107683,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T19:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}